## Commit messages
Format: `type(scope): description`

Types: `feat` | `fix` | `refactor` | `chore` | `docs` | `test` | `perf` | `ci`  
`scope` is optional (module or area).

```
feat(auth): add GitHub OAuth login
fix(api): correct pagination offset for user list
refactor: extract form validation hook
```

- Subject matches repo language (EN/ZH); no trailing period
- One concern per commit; do not mix features and refactors

## Branch names
`type/short-topic` in kebab-case

```
feat/github-oauth
fix/pagination-offset
refactor/form-validation-hook
```

## PR descriptions (when asked)
- One sentence on what changed
- Up to five key files
- Prefix breaking changes with ⚠️
- No filler
